Package io.crums.sldg.entry

Class EntryInfo

java.lang.Object
io.crums.sldg.entry.EntryInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<EntryInfo>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EntryPackBuilder.MetaEntry
public class EntryInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<EntryInfo>
Partial information about an entry. It is not named Meta.. because it doesn't yet have extra information about an entry; but a subclass could change that (see for example #name()).

Equality and comparison semantics are governed solely by row number. Instances are immutable.
